summary: My first attempt at a small house that has all you need.
descriptionHtml:
My first attempt at a small house that has all you need. It was a good learning experience working with the creation kit, and I may or may not update this house as I realize it\'s not perfect, nor is it the most aesthetically pleasing house to choose from.

The house entrance can be found on an island in the middle of a lake slightly north of Falkreath. The door is in the side of a rock-face and is stone, so it doesn\'t stick out like a sore thumb.

If you have any suggestions of things that I could work on in the house, feel free to leave a comment! 

P.S.    I do realaize that the ebony rocks in the mine do not currently function as they should, but I may look into that in the near future.
author: lordofpizza
